title: American Cinematographer - November 2013
description:
American Cinematographer - November 2013

116 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 31 MB 


The magazine focuses on the art and craft of cinematography, covering domestic and international film productions.  The magazine includes interviews with cinematographers, directors and production colleagues, as well as historical articles, technical how-to pieces, and discussion of tools and technologies that affect cinematography.
